author: Henry J. Gomez, cleveland.com
title: Indivisible town hall attendees take on the absent Rob Portman at Cleveland church (video)
text: The evening offered a peek into the discontent brewing in the early days of President Donald Trump's administration. Indivisible and other groups are calling on members of Congress to oppose -- or "resist," to use the phrase the movement's followers prefer -- Trump's agenda.
